        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "x": 20,
          "y": 196,
          "content": "On attention, systems, and the art of noticing",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fill": "rgba(28,25,23,0.42)",
          "fontWeight": 400,
          "fontFamily": "Georgia",
          "textAnchor": "start",
          "letterSpacing": 0,
          "opacity": 1,
          "fontStyle": "italic"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "x1": 20,
          "y1": 210,
          "x2": 370,
          "y2": 210,
          "stroke": "rgba(28,25,23,0.10)",
          "strokeWidth": 1,
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "x": 20,
          "y": 234,
          "content": "This week I found myself returning to a question I",
          "fontSize": 14,
          "fill": "#1C1917",
          "fontWeight": 400,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "textAnchor": "start",
          "letterSpacing": 0,
          "opacity": 1,
          "fontStyle": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "x": 20,
          "y": 256,
          "content": "first encountered in Epstein's Range: what do the",
          "fontSize": 14,
          "fill": "#1C1917",
          "fontWeight": 400,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "textAnchor": "start",
          "letterSpacing": 0,
          "opacity": 1,
          "fontStyle": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "x": 20,
          "y": 278,
          "content": "best generalists actually do with their breadth?",
          "fontSize": 14,
          "fill": "#1C1917",
          "fontWeight": 400,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "textAnchor": "start",
          "letterSpacing": 0,
          "opacity": 1,
          "fontStyle": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "x": 20,
          "y": 308,
          "content": "The naive answer is synthesis — they combine ideas",
          "fontSize": 14,
          "fill": "#1C1917",
          "fontWeight": 400,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "textAnchor": "start",
          "letterSpacing": 0,
          "opacity": 1,
          "fontStyle": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "x": 20,
          "y": 330,
          "content": "across domains. But the deeper answer seems to be",
          "fontSize": 14,
          "fill": "#1C1917",
          "fontWeight": 400,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "textAnchor": "start",
          "letterSpacing": 0,
          "opacity": 1,
          "fontStyle": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "x": 20,
          "y": 352,
          "content": "about a different kind of attention.",
          "fontSize": 14,
          "fill": "#1C1917",
          "fontWeight": 400,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "textAnchor": "start",
          "letterSpacing": 0,
          "opacity": 1,
          "fontStyle": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "x": 20,
          "y": 382,
          "content": "KEY INSIGHT",
          "fontSize": 10,
          "fill": "#C4522A",
          "fontWeight": 700,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "textAnchor": "start",
          "letterSpacing": 1.2,
          "opacity": 1,
          "fontStyle": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "x": 20,
          "y": 400,
          "content": "Experts notice anomalies; novices see averages.",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fill": "#1C1917",
          "fontWeight": 400,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "textAnchor": "start",
          "letterSpacing": 0,
          "opacity": 1,
          "fontStyle": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "x": 20,
          "y": 421,
          "content": "The habit of noticing deviation is trainable.",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fill": "#1C1917",
          "fontWeight": 400,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "textAnchor": "start",
          "letterSpacing": 0,
          "opacity": 1,
          "fontStyle": "normal"
        },
